ii.  Content, particularly with regard to substances that might produce an environmental or social
impact;
iii.   Safe use of the product or service;
iv.  Disposal of the product and environmental or social impacts;
v.   Other (explain).
b.   Percentage of significant product or service categories covered by and assessed for compliance with
such procedures.

